text: Willelm king gret þomas arcebiscop & Þurold & Earnwig his scyrgerefan & ealle þa þegnas on Snotingeham scype & on Lincolscyre frencisce & englisce freondlice.

And ic kyðe eow þæt ic an Sancte Marian æt Stowe & þan munecan Niweweorce & Fladburh & Brantune & Wylle Wepentæc, mid sace & mid socne & tolle & teame swaforforð swa Godgyfe on Eadweardes dæge kynges fyrmest hæfde on eallan þingan.
And þa Remig biscop gesweotelian mæg þæt <rihtlice> þær to gebyrige & ic beode þæt cume in ongean swa hwæt swa is ut gedon & nan oðer.
